Users Just Being Users
Purchasing power is a reflection of usefulness. As user volume increases, on-chain spending sustains the growth, sustainability and decentralization of mining operations.

"The current system where every user is a network node is not the intended configuration for large scale. That would be like every Usenet user [running] their own NNTP server. The design supports letting users just be users. The more burden it is to run a node, the fewer nodes there will be. Those few nodes will be big server farms. The rest will be client nodes that only do transactions and don't generate." ‚Äî Satoshi

